lead_paragraph: Brock Osweiler took one last dig at Denver's fans after Houston's 27-9 loss to the Broncos. He figured they would "be a little bit louder with the boos."

headline.print_headline: Denver Gives Osweiler Rude Welcome in 27-9 Win Over Houston
